h3. Problem Definition
We are using pages with 100+ images attached to them.
On another page, we try to insert a few of those images by using the "!" marco -> Open File Library -> Search on other pages.
When typing in the first digits of the file name (our filenames are like this pattern: ###########.jpg or .png) and hitting Search the thumbnail list gets generated. If there are many images with the same starting tag, only a selection of them appears, the others aren't shown. The selection is always limitted to 50 results.
{code:borderStyle=solid}
spaceKey=&query=1_IMG_&search=name&type=attachment&groupResults=true&maxResultsPerGroup=50&searchParentName=true&pageSize=50&_=1472124401868
{code}

h3. Suggested Solution

Add the possibility to modify the limit of the search results in the file macro.

