Plugins are able to implement their own transformers using the {{<transformer>}} module. Confluence Mobile, however, uses its own list of transformers that doesn't look at those provided by plugins.

For example, the images from the {{confluence-hipchat-emoticons-plugin}} will not render at all on Confluence Mobile.
